  "title": "🦅 Sales & Recruitment Trainee (Fresh Grads Welcome!)",
  "description": "<p>🚀 <strong>Kick-start Your Career with Euphoria Organization!</strong></p><p>Just finished school or graduated and not sure where to start? This is for you.</p><p>At <strong>Euphoria Organization</strong>, we don’t look for experience — we look for <strong>attitude, hunger, and growth mindset</strong>.</p><p><strong>What you’ll do:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Learn sales & marketing skills hands-on</p></li><li><p>Be involved in recruitment & team building</p></li><li><p>Communicate with real clients (not boring theory work)</p></li><li><p>Grow from trainee to leadership roles</p></li></ul><p><strong>Why join us?</strong><br />✨ Full training provided<br />✨ Fast career progression<br />✨ Young, energetic team culture<br />✨ Performance-based income<br />✨ Personal development & leadership exposure</p><p><strong>Who should apply?</strong></p><ul><li><p>NSF / fresh grads / career switches</p></li><li><p>Outgoing or willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Goal-driven and open to challenges</p></li><li><p>No experience needed</p></li></ul><p>📍 Based in a fast-paced, supportive environment<br />📈 Your growth = our priority</p><p>👉 Ready to level up instead of settling?<br />Apply now and start building your future with <strong>Euphoria Organization</strong>.</p>",
